OL,3,CDoctor 'stabbed by fellow surgeon'
OL,4,Cfelt intestines bulging out, trial told
OL,6,FA doctor alleged to have been attacked
OL,7,Fby a fellow plastic surgeon at his
OL,8,Fhome in Nottinghamshire has told a
OL,9,Fjury how he was stabbed by a "figure"
OL,10,Fin darkness outside his conservatory,
OL,11,Fand then clutched his abdomen to feel
OL,12,Fhis intestines bulging out.
OL,14,FGraeme Perks was questioned by a
OL,15,Flawyer appointed to avoid him being
OL,16,Fcross-examined by his colleague Peter
OL,17,FBrooks, who denies attempted murder,
OL,18,Fattempted arson with intent to
OL,19,Fendanger life, and unlawful possession
OL,20,Fof a knife.
