OL,3,CDoctor 'stabbed by fellow surgeon'
OL,4,Cfelt intestines bulging out, trial told
OL,6,FJurors sitting at Loughborough
OL,7,FCourthouse have heard that Mr Perks
OL,8,Fsuffered "extremely life-threatening"
OL,9,Finjuries to his liver, intestines and
OL,10,Fpancreas in the early hours of January
OL,11,F14 2021 after being confronted by an
OL,12,Fintruder at his home in Halam, near
OL,13,FSouthwell, in Nottinghamshire.
OL,15,FGiving evidence to the court, Mr Perks
OL,16,Fdenied that he had picked up a crowbar
OL,17,Fbefore his assailant, whom he wrongly
OL,18,Fmistook for his youngest son, turned
OL,19,Fand stabbed him.
