OL,6,FAsked by the barrister if he recalled
OL,7,Fhaving picked up the crowbar before he
OL,8,Fwent outside, Mr Perks said: "No. I
OL,9,Fhave never seen that crowbar in my
OL,10,Flife. I have no recollection of that
OL,11,Fcrowbar."
OL,13,FProviding further details of the night
OL,14,FBrooks is alleged to have tried to
OL,15,Fkill him, Mr Perks added: "I realised
OL,16,Fsomething was seriously amiss.
