OL,6,F"I found this figure outside. I came
OL,7,Fupon a figure at the back, facing
OL,8,Ftowards me on the grass. I don't know
OL,9,Fwhether the figure was stationary or
OL,10,Fmoving."
OL,12,FEstimating that the figure was around
OL,13,F2-3 feet away at the time he suffered
OL,14,Fa knife wound, Mr Perks told the
OL,15,Fcourt: "I didn't know I had been
OL,16,Fstabbed. I made a deduction.
OL,18,F"I have no recollection of the knife
OL,19,For the crowbar. My recollection is all
OL,20,FI felt was guts sticking out."
