OL,11,FMr Leslie asked Mr Perks: "The fact is
OL,12,Fyou were so discombobulated at that
OL,13,Fstage you actually believed that it
OL,14,Fwas (the youngest son) that had done
OL,15,Fthis wicked act?"
OL,17,FMr Perks, who was aged 65 at the time
OL,18,Fof the attack and had only recently
OL,19,Fretired, replied: "Correct."
