OL,6,FUnder further questioning by
OL,7,Fprosecutor Tracy Ayling KC, Mr Perks
OL,8,Fwas asked if he had anything in his
OL,9,Fhands when he went to feel his wounds.
OL,11,FMr Perks answered: "I think I turned
OL,12,Fback to the house. My recollection is
OL,13,Fthat my bare hands grasped the area of
OL,14,Fthe blow and felt the bulge.
OL,16,F"Sadly I am experienced enough to
OL,17,Frecognise that it was intestine."
