OL,6,FA consultant surgeon who operated to
OL,7,Ftreat Mr Perks' injuries at
OL,8,FNottingham's Queen's Medical Centre
OL,9,Fsaid the wounds to the victim's organs
OL,10,Fwere "way up in the most serious"
OL,11,Fcategory of those he had treated, with
OL,12,Fa 95% chance of death.
OL,14,FThe court heard 40 units of blood and
OL,15,Fblood product were used to treat Mr
OL,16,FPerks, who lost an estimated six
OL,17,Flitres of blood.
