OL,6,FThe court has heard that the
OL,7,Fdefendant, formerly of Landseer Road,
OL,8,FSouthwell, has chosen not to attend
OL,9,Fhis trial and not to have legal
OL,10,Frepresentation.
OL,12,FProsecutors say the 61-year-old doused
OL,13,Fthe ground floor of Mr Perks' property
OL,14,Fin petrol before knifing his former
OL,15,Fcolleague, who he "hated" because he
OL,16,Fwas giving evidence in a work
OL,17,Fdisciplinary hearing against the
OL,18,Fdefendant.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
